Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace is not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy, I know. I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}But it's too risky to go to Gray Terminal now\Nsince you're wounded and there are troops everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,--But...!\N--It was a big fire! And chances are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...slim but we all want to believe \Nthat the boss and Ace are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogra went there to look for \Nthem now so trust him and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's having a hard \Ntime - not just you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--The fishing boat has been hit!\N--How's the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He made the Celestial Dragon mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! The ship is catching fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they shoot me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Jalmack! There is a child on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone flies a black flag, he's \Na pirate regardless of who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A commoner shouldn't cross \Nthe path of my ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What was that ship doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an important ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't wanna put\Nthe Celestial Dragon in a bad mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the shipwreck already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace... Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She's severely wounded! \NHurry up and treat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think that I was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--But...!\N--Why are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not dead, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy is just happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you about the night of the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After we left with Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened to you and boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought against Bluejam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And we barely defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And we tried to follow you guys right away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but the fire was blocking our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! There's no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wait!\N--What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice since I told them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd take responsibility \Nfor bringing you home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow my lead. Don't get \Nseparated at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dadan! Are you alright, Dadan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it through the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nbut Dadan got severely burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to get to\Nthe riverside in Middlewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with me! You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the town to steal some \Nmedicine and get something to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and tried to save Dadan's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry \Nabout me so just go, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap! I thought you were \Nresponsible for bringing me home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Some survivors could be around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone get away! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, we see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, \NI'm glad that you both survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe what \Nhappened to Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sabo is worrying about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--Banzai!\N--Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Another rude commoner could \Nappear at any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,--Watch carefully.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how's Sabo doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad that Ace is back \Nand Dadan is recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help getting fired up sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always afraid that if I run,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave something important behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy was behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know but I think that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when he faced a cloud \Nof enemies beyond his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger would never run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he suicidal? Running \Naway is a strategy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right but he'd never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he'd leave the \Npeople he loved behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If he ran, he would put his crew in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, "he wouldn't run \Naway" isn't quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't let the enemy have \Na chance to go after his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd change into a sort of \Ndemon in those situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He once destroyed a country's entire military
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because they talked badly about his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd become violent when angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,\NHe was short-tempered and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was naive and straightforward \Nlike a child at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because his early life was like Ace's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He hated to lose those he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He was that reckless but he survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and became the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:12:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he got a bad reputation, \Nhis crew trusted him implicitly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I as a Navy soldier \Ncouldn't help respecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to take care of Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones taking care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Have something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of the world still hate Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And while Ace hates his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it really is "like father, like son."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's see which \None of you will win...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking for Ace and Dadan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?! Sabo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop lying, you fool! \NDon't even joke about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying or joking \Nabout it! It was so sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I could barely believe what I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Sabo went back to his family's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he be at sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! He went home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A hoodlum like me can \Nunderstand how he feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't always wanna \Ngo back to their home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was really happy, \Nhe wouldn't go out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't go out to sea by himself \Nwith a black flag on his ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was all by myself even if I had parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why didn't we go \Nthere to take him back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the guy who killed \NSabo now?! I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kill the Celestial Dragon?! \NThat's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make him pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Move...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so confident even \Nthough you're not that strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do?! They'll just kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die and people will \Nforget you by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a nameless kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo was killed by this country! This world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father changed the world by his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When you become a man that important,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie this fool up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Stop crying like a girl, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to your senses, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--Untie him.\N--Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--Where's Luffy?\N--He's been crying all night and he's sleeping now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! You're not gonna believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a letter from Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:55.97,"Sign",,0,0,0,,{\an9}"To my brothers on Mt. Corvo\NFrom Sabo"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've sent it before he went out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna go to the town! \NIt's for us, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ace, Luffy, I hope you guys \Nweren't hurt in the fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm worrying about you both but \NI believe that you're okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry to say it, guys, but when you \Nget this letter, I'll already be..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"...out on the sea."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Things led to things and I decided \Nto set out to sea before you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"My destination will be anywhere but here."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm gonna become stronger \Nand become a pirate!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"The three of us have to become \Nthe freest pirates ever."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"One day, let's meet up again somewhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Somewhere on the wide open sea! \NDefinitely, someday!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"By the way, Ace, which of us \Ndo you think is the bigger brother?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Two big brothers and one little brother."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's odd but our brotherhood \Nis my treasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Luffy is still a weak crybaby but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"...he is our little brother \Nso take good care of him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they call themselves \Nobservers?! They're partying everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't covered Sabo's story...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that his parents didn't take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,His parents are nobles
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're powerless against the World \NGovernment and Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Luffy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He still isn't eating much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But he still eats twice as much as we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Sabo's death really got to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta set out to sea someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of this \Ncountry and live freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer are you gonna lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasure that we were hiding \Nin the forest is all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The survivors from Bluejam's crew took \Nit or maybe the military found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't care about the treasure anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the pirate savings that \NI was gonna share with Sabo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but Sabo didn't need it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll just let it go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use having treasure \Nif you can't even protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ace... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,More, and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,More, more and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna become even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can protect anything or anyone! \NI don't have to lose anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! Worry about yourself first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're far weaker than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo told me to take care of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise that I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I leave a wimpy \Nbrother like you behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not smart so I don't quite \Nknow what really killed Sabo yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it must be something opposed to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo died before he knew freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We exchanged that same cup \Nof sake and we're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So listen, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to live without leaving any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys from noble family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...will become full nobles when they turn 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need to leave here by 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta go out to sea someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and live as we like. \NFreer than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we'll make enemies of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the old man will become our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta risk everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.73,0:22:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out to sea at 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And we will become... pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and Ace are stricken with grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.12,0:23:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but they hold on to their \Ndream of becoming pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and set off toward the future again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Their day of departure will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To achieve the dream that \NSabo was unable to realize!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"In Order to Keep the Promise \NTheir Separate Departures!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
